The Miniproject is thought to work with udp-streaming. But as the Simulator and the database cannot be shared because of propery reason 
example data is provided in ItcsData and the template MinirojectNifiFile.xml is provided.

1. Get Apache NIFI https://nifi.apache.org/download.html
2. Run NIFI ..nifi-1.1.2\bin\run-nifi.bat
3. Import Template MiniProjectNifiGetFile.xml  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HU5_3PlNmtQ
4. Right click GetFile - Configure - Properties - Input Directory {change to ItcsData-Folder of Source}
5. Right click ExecuteScript - Configure - Properties - Script File {change to filter0gps.js of Source}

1. Configure Mail in application.properties
2. Recompile
3. start 


available Sites:
http://localhost:8443/sum.html
http://localhost:8443/busses.html
